OL,3,CMarks and Spencer says cyber attack
OL,4,Clikely to cost #300m and last till July
OL,6,FMarks & Spencer has said disruption
OL,7,Ffrom a major cyber attack is expected
OL,8,Fto continue through to July and cost
OL,9,Fthe company around #300 million.
OL,11,FThe high street retailer was targeted
OL,12,Fby hackers around Easter weekend and
OL,13,Fhas seen issues with contactless
OL,14,Fpayments, click and collect orders,
OL,15,Fempty shelves and the halting of all
OL,16,Fonline orders.
OL,18,FThe retailer revealed on Wednesday
OL,19,Fmorning that online sales and profits
OL,20,Fin its fashion, home and beauty
OL,21,Fbusiness have been "heavily impacted".
