OL,6,FChief executive Stuart Machin said:
OL,7,F"It has been challenging, but it is a
OL,8,Fmoment in time, and we are now focused
OL,9,Fon recovery, with the aim of exiting
OL,10,Fthis period a much stronger business.
OL,12,F"There is no change to our strategy
OL,13,Fand our longer-term plans to reshape
OL,14,FM&S for growth and, if anything, the
OL,15,Fincident allows us to accelerate the
OL,16,Fpace of change as we draw a line and
OL,17,Fmove on."
